{"tid":2160581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話香港警甴冇好似Belarus咁樣倒戈「係因為有解放軍」係咪忘記咗烏克蘭革命嘅後續？","createTime":"2020-08-17T05:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T15:13:53.000Z","uid":131691,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cde1e4f94b5ef989caee98f74f774e7e27ad1d02","tid":2160581,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭革命成功驅趕領袖後，俄羅斯派軍入城「拯救」俄羅斯人民，吞併烏克蘭部分領土。<br />\n<br />\n白俄羅斯/白羅斯而家面對嘅嘢其實一樣：軟弱嘅歐盟+唔會hesitate出兵，想重建蘇聯嘅俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再用「有解放軍」「香港唔係權力核心」嚟幫香港警甴解話，人哋Belarus嘅警察真係面對俄羅斯軍隊嘅威脅都選擇企係人民嘅一邊，係真男人。<br />\n<br />\n唔似香港班陽痿警甴。"},{"pid":"952d596f521ffa3453a30ce20f5d6e87983ff3e0","tid":2160581,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4266168c29330eccfab94f8ebfd141c9876f95","tid":2160581,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b4687bad5ccb2cf856a0ee6a5e95a15a5cb632","tid":2160581,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f9564d0827e6ae3ea635cbcd202ae90aa58088","tid":2160581,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"c62665a24e1c239fb4d81637ca4e05d729962c55","tid":2160581,"uid":231583,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0a70a37b5ac0eb5331659042f362ea84cccb5e6","tid":2160581,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62665a24e1c239fb4d81637ca4e05d729962c55","tid":2160581,"uid":231583,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔少人喺Belarus嘅po裡面有咁講"},{"pid":"08e554c41020d3e3f881c905e6cde524f91ea8aa","tid":2160581,"uid":321859,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"佢地唔會倒戈唔係咁簡單三言兩語講得通<br />\n係要由成個社會構造開始拆解<br />\n<br />\n一來警隊依家好多非香港人 好多係中国落黎<br />\n<br />\n二來香港公務員份人工 可以拋離其他工種<br />\n打個比喻 舊年區議會大勝班素人<br />\n拎3萬人工 3萬出去打份普通工其實都可能有<br />\n低都係低幾k 個差距唔大 都仲有資格講下理想<br />\n反觀立法會果10皮野 班泛民出到去搵唔到呢個數 結果都係為左份糧屎都食 仲講咩抗爭<br />\n<br />\n三來 宿舍問題 呢啲唔講啦 細路都明<br />\n<br />\n你要班冇乜點讀過書既差佬 放棄4萬月入<br />\n同共產黨比佢地既權力 為左一個香港夢<br />\n<br />\n真係彩你都有味"},{"pid":"f0a84c8e0098525d5c68b6aacdc50bae60e1f63d","tid":2160581,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9af7695d1a607dbab2d8ed93a17971783766ffc4","tid":2160581,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"得一兩條友講呢個point<br />\n大部分人都係話佢地無撚腦同為人工喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2737f5a5cb6f7d34b70b2a938c9db2e2fbd5b737","tid":2160581,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0a70a37b5ac0eb5331659042f362ea84cccb5e6","tid":2160581,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62665a24e1c239fb4d81637ca4e05d729962c55","tid":2160581,"uid":231583,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔少人喺Belarus嘅po裡面有咁講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"睇過<br />\n我琴日開post得一條友講<br />\n哪來的唔少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46b2814267f5c3c612707cf9bd4f2bececa0f6d","tid":2160581,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"以班散仔嘅學歷<br />\n出去應該搵得一半錢"},{"pid":"00e3943b546173e514e3122b661eae7a47cea086","tid":2160581,"uid":16846